vote.title: Authorize a three-year consultant service contract, with two one-year renewal options, for benefits consulting and auditing services of medical and pharmacy benefit plans for the Department of Human Resources - Holmes Murphy & Associates, LLC, most advantageous proposer of six - Not to exceed $837,750 - Financing:  Employee Benefits Fund (subject to annual appropriations)
